_sText:
A fairly dark, easy bunny hop map. Will take around 30 seconds to finish.
Consists of 4 levels: 
- regular 
- with height increase
- a slope for speed gain
- with large platforms for high speed strafing

This map doesn't contain any triggers and teleports. So it's kinda one try one run type.
